{"tid":1233553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想輸？有以下大方向可考慮下","createTime":"2019-06-16T19:30:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T09:38:01.000Z","uid":67249,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8cc76f2fda3e4e29b7316db2e9739c76b5aac13e","tid":1233553,"uid":67249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:30:31.000Z","msg":"我覺得大家要開始組織下啲軟性工作，滲入民間，將團火keep住<br />\n<br />\n以下為大方向<br />\n<br />\n1.） 組織挑動建制派內部矛盾<br />\n2.） 收集證據，控告同追究黑警<br />\n3.） 干擾建制派部署<br />\n4.） 繼續從不同渠道發聲，鼓動群眾向政府表達撤銷義士控罪同撤銷定性為暴動<br />\n5.） 繼續利用輿論向政府施壓，要求撤回修定<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家團結，keep住個力量</span></span><br />\n<br />\n不妨大家交換下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b547195da1c6735964cd166643e147fe750650","tid":1233553,"uid":67249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1776a74a3c13ac7dc0f687c5abb4d70b9f2609a","tid":1233553,"uid":237888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cc76f2fda3e4e29b7316db2e9739c76b5aac13e","tid":1233553,"uid":67249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:30:31.000Z","msg":"我覺得大家要開始組織下啲軟性工作，滲入民間，將團火keep住<br />\n<br />\n以下為大方向<br />\n<br />\n1.） 組織挑動建制派內部矛盾<br />\n2.） 收集證據，控告同追究黑警<br />\n3.） 干擾建制派部署<br />\n4.） 繼續從不同渠道發聲，鼓動群眾向政府表達撤銷義士控罪同撤銷定性為暴動<br />\n5.） 繼續利用輿論向政府施壓，要求撤回修定<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家團結，keep住個力量</span></span><br />\n<br />\n不妨大家交換下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T19:39:44.000Z","msg":"幫推btw<br />\n致70後<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1233361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1233361</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n好有同感"},{"pid":"e2b69cdc299d2b28d9c4758c87053fadbc462d9b","tid":1233553,"uid":87780,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"c